            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C.) *In nomine sancte et individue trinitatis. <persName ref="#people/3578" key="#Emperor/king #marriage"
                            >Lottharius</persName> (I) divina favente clementia tertius Romanorum
                            <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus.* Cum lubrici seculi
                        conditio brevis est et incerta, admonemur, ut in hac valle lacrimarum, dum
                        tempus habemus, seramus quod in futuro cum gaudio metamus. Quapropter
                        omnibus Christi nostrisque fidelibus tam futuris quam presentibus notum
                        fieri volumus, qualiter nos pro dei amore et interventu <rs key="#marriage">contectalis</rs>
                        nostre <persName ref="#people/3701" key="#marriage #Intercessory">RICHINZĘ</persName>
                        <rs>imperatricis</rs> et pro animę nostrę nostrorumque parentum salute ac
                        imperii nostri stabilitate pro rogatu etiam et <rs key="#Intercessory"
                            >peticione</rs> consortis nostrę prefatę ob interventum quoque <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Abbots #Monasteries" ref="#people/3568"
                            >Heinrici</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Forests #Immunity"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">sancti Benedicti de Larione</orgName> et
                        omnium fratrum suorum, quorum fraternitatem diligimus, omnes <geogName
                            key="#Forests" ref="#estates/2094"><rs key="#Forests">buscos</rs> de
                                <placeName key="#Forests" ref="#places/34"
                                    >Pigugnaga</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus quę <persName ref="#people/3707"
                            key="#Forests">Hugizo</persName> in <rs>pignore</rs> habuit et tenuit,
                        eidem monasterio concedimus et donamus ac imperiali auctoritate confirmamus,
                        ut idem monasterium habeat et teneat in perpetuum libere <rs key="#Immunity"
                            >sine alicuius exactione. Precipimus ergo, ut nullus archiepiscopus
                            episcopus marchio comes vicecomes scultatius castaldio vicedominus nec
                            etiam aliquis noster nostrorumque successorum missus predictum
                            monasterium de supradictis rebus quas pro remissione peccatorum
                            nostrorum eidem concessimus, inquietare molestare vel divestire
                            audeat</rs>. Si quis vero, quod absit, huius <rs
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">nostri scripti paginam</rs> temerario ausu
                        infringere temptaverit, <rs key="#Penalty">auri libras viginti</rs>
                        componat, medietatem <rs key="#Camera_regis">camere nostre</rs> et
                        medietatem prefato sancti Benedicti loco. Quod ut verius credatur et ab
                        omnibus inviolabiliter custodiatur, hanc cartam inde conscriptam et manu
                        propria corroboratam impressione nostri sigilli insigniri iussimus. *Signum
                        domni Lottharii tertii Romanorum (M.) imperatoris invictissimi.* *Ego
                        <persName key="#Imperial/royal_diploma" ref="#people/3706">Berhthaldus</persName> vice <persName ref="#people/3705" key="#Archchancellor #Imperial/royal_diploma">Adelberti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Archchancellor">archicancellarii</rs> recognovi.* Data anno
                        incarnationis dominicę M.C.XXX.V, III nonis decembris, indictione XIII, anno
                        vero regni regis Lottharii XI, imperii III. Actum <placeName key="#Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            ref="#places/4145">Goslarie</placeName>; in Christi nomine feliciter
                        amen. </ab>
